(3597, 285, 'first_col', 'The Honorable E. Wayne Bachus of Temple, Texas, is a former Judge of Bell County, Texas, and has more than 30 years of experience as a practicing attorney in Texas, focusing on general business matters. Judge Bachus has served on numerous boards, including the State Bar of Texas, and served multiple terms as the president of Texas Association of Court at Law Judges. He is also an adjunct instructor at Temple College. He holds a Bachelor of Arts from The University of Texas at Austin and a Juris Doctor from Baylor University School of Law.\r\n\r\nTerm: May 8, 2023 - March 1, 2025'),
