(3773, 274, 'flexible_content_2_text', 'We are the largest healthcare quality improvement organization in the United States and trusted adviser to the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS). We have a unique understanding of beneficiaries and have developed programs that improve patient outcomes, increase satisfaction, and drastically reduce readmissions.\r\n\r\nWith technology at its core, Livanta has built a portfolio of telehealth, data analytics, and tracking mechanisms that position it to inspire a better healthcare system that connects patients, providers, and payers to improve health outcomes, increase efficiency, and manage costs.'),
