(5294, 223, 'flexible_content_6_slider_2_text', 'The ANSI National Accreditation Board (ANAB) is the largest multidisciplinary accreditation body in North America. ANAB is a nongovernmental organization that provides accreditation services and training to public- and private-sector organizations and is owned by the American National Standards Institute (ANSI).'),
