(8924, 407, 'flexible_content_4_dropdown_1_col_left', 'The Livanta healthcare analytic team provides its extensive expertise in econometrics, statistics, and clinical healthcare to help government agencies decipher trends in health care improvement, identify key insights into program changes, and delineate healthcare impacts of policy decisions. As modeling experts, the Livanta Team navigates Medicare claims, medical record review outcomes, and other administrative healthcare data with advanced statistical techniques to analyze the effectiveness, efficiency, and equity of national and state healthcare systems and to assist government agencies achieve their goals. Our experience modeling healthcare data applies continuous and discrete dependent variables using quasi-experimental, cross-sectional, longitudinal, clustering, and hierarchical/multi-level approaches.'),
(8925, 407, '_flexible_content_4_dropdown_1_col_left', 'field_6599480ae00a9'),
