(11099, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_title', 'Software Engineering'),
(11100, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_title', 'field_659db96fe0331'),
(11101, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_col_left', 'Livanta provides a disciplined approach to designing, developing, and deploying software. Referred to as the Livanta™ Software Engineering Process (LSP), Livanta’s approach ensures that its software products are developed on predictable schedules and budgets and meet public sector agencies\' needs. LSP encapsulates the best practices in software development and is suitable for a wide range of projects. Software best practices are proven approaches to software development that position the software development team to deliver quality software successfully on time and within budget. The LSP is based upon five software best practices:\r\n1. Iterative Software Development\r\n2. Active Requirements Management\r\n3. Architecture-Centric Approach\r\n4. Verify Software Quality\r\n5. Software Change Management'),
(11102, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_col_left', 'field_659db96fe0332'),
(11103, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_col_right', 'Value Proposition\r\nLivanta’s expertise in software engineering and use of best practices establishes repeatable, measurable, and predictable environments in which mission-critical software systems are developed, giving clients the peace of mind that systems will be delivered on time and within budget.'),
(11104, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_0_col_right', 'field_659db96fe0333'),
(11105, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_title', 'Hosting/Cloud Computing'),
(11106, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_title', 'field_659db96fe0331'),
(11107, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_left', 'The Livanta™ Innovation Cloud (LIC) meets vigorous system security requirements of state and federal government contracts to provide an ultra-fast, cloud-based application development hosting infrastructure as a service (IaaS) offering.'),
(11108, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_left', 'field_659db96fe0332'),
(11109, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_right', 'Value Proposition\r\nLivanta designed the LIC with security, scalability, and reliability in mind. The long-term operating cost is lower than that of a system with physical hardware investment. In addition, the LIC design assumes redundancy by design, dramatically reducing the likelihood of system downtime.'),
(11110, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_right', 'field_659db96fe0333'),
(11111, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_title', 'Website Development and Maintenance'),
(11112, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_title', 'field_659db96fe0331'),
(11113, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_col_left', 'Livanta has years of experience building web solutions for public sector healthcare agencies. Livanta uses its mastery of web services and web-based automation services for various applications. This includes websites and web applications for public-facing healthcare portals, enterprise dashboards, as well as case management and workflow solutions. Livanta’s engaging website designs leverage 2D/3D design that will captivate clients. Livanta takes advantage of APIs like the Web Graphics Library (WebGL) and Open Graphics Library (OpenGL) to provide an appealing look and feel to Livanta’s developed websites. JavaScript and CSS frameworks like Animate.css, Bounce.js, and Magic Animations are employed to give clients the cleanest look and feel.'),
(11114, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_col_left', 'field_659db96fe0332'),
(11115, 487, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_col_right', 'Value Proposition\r\nLivanta’s digital expertise providing computer services to public sector agencies at the federal and state-levels and its years of experience building web solutions ensures that clients get solutions that work and are well received by beneficiaries and citizens.'),
(11116, 487, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_2_col_right', 'field_659db96fe0333'),
