(11176, 511, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_left', 'field_659db96fe0332'),
(11177, 511, 'flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_right', 'Value Proposition\r\nLivanta designed the LIC with security, scalability, and reliability in mind. The long-term operating cost is lower than that of a system with physical hardware investment. In addition, the LIC design assumes redundancy by design, dramatically reducing the likelihood of system downtime.'),
(11178, 511, '_flexible_content_3_dropdown_1_col_right', 'field_659db96fe0333'),
