(11323, 519, 'flexible_content_4_tabs_2_content', 'The Livanta™ Data Analytics Platform (LDAP) is an integrated collection of tools that allows Livanta to mine, assess, infer, and report on a multitude of data sources. Livanta leverages a wide array of data sources from organizations, such as the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS), state departments of health, and commercial data repositories to establish dynamic data warehouses that offer unique insights into healthcare. Livanta uses artificial intelligence, machine learning, and conventional tools to assemble and generate tangible findings quickly.'),
