(11341, 519, 'flexible_content_4_tabs_5_content', 'Trustfolio™ Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) system consists of a tightly integrated portfolio of software applications hosted in a central environment, using a central database, and designed to automate business processes. The business applications portfolio includes human resources, accounting, proposal pricing, project budgeting, contract management, and analytics and reporting.\r\n\r\nThe Trustfolio™ ERP includes two-way integration with QuickBooks using a middleware component called the Accounting System Broker (ASB). The ASB currently supports QuickBooks and is designed to connect to additional accounting systems in the future. Trustfolio™ uses the Workuments software applications to support human resources functions.'),
