(11571, 492, '_flexible_content_2_title', 'field_658f1148e07a8'),
(11572, 492, 'flexible_content_2_text', 'We empower patients and caregivers, helping them navigate the healthcare system with knowledge and respect.\r\n\r\nEngaging directly with patients and their families, Livanta offers a patient-centered approach to case review and advocacy services. Livanta\'s skilled clinical staff empowers patients to make informed decisions regarding their plans of care and to navigate their care transitions effectively.'),
