(11590, 492, 'flexible_content_2_list_2_desc', 'Offering cultural and linguistic competence as the largest Medicare Quality Improvement Organization (QIO), Livanta’s professionals provide navigation and review services to help persons and their caregivers overcome health and wellness barriers across the full care continuum.'),
