(11635, 492, '_flexible_content_4_list_1_icon', 'field_658f2e6c21bbd'),
(11636, 492, 'flexible_content_4_list_1_desc', 'Working quickly and with the highest level of quality, Livanta aligns existing efforts to advance health, improve care, and reduce costs.'),
(11637, 492, '_flexible_content_4_list_1_desc', 'field_658f2e7c21bbe'),
(11638, 492, 'flexible_content_4_list_2_icon', '87'),
(11639, 492, '_flexible_content_4_list_2_icon', 'field_658f2e6c21bbd'),
(11640, 492, 'flexible_content_4_list_2_desc', 'Serving in varying payment error evaluation and management roles, Livanta promotes accuracy of error rate determination and correction, such as our contracted accomplishments for the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) with error rate measurement and reduction.'),
(11641, 492, '_flexible_content_4_list_2_desc', 'field_658f2e7c21bbe'),
(11642, 492, 'flexible_content_4_list_3_icon', '88'),
(11643, 492, '_flexible_content_4_list_3_icon', 'field_658f2e6c21bbd'),
(11644, 492, 'flexible_content_4_list_3_desc', 'As a Beneficiary and Family Centered Care - Quality Improvement Organization (BFCC-QIO) contractor for CMS, Livanta innovated the Person and Family Engagement (PFE) program, which reduced hospital 30-day readmissions by 80.7% under Livanta’s workload. The largest QIO for Medicare, Livanta continues to impact health care outcomes.'),
