(11655, 492, '_flexible_content_5_title', 'field_658f33e02a567'),
(11656, 492, 'flexible_content_5_text', 'We provide governmental agencies with public policy insights through actuarial and econometric analysis.\r\n\r\nLivanta provides expert data management, statistical analysis, and econometric modeling for policy evaluation. With deep industry expertise, Livanta helps governmental agencies monitor current trends in healthcare improvement and recognize impacts of policy decisions.'),
