(217, 1, '2024-01-03 20:45:33', '2024-01-03 20:45:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Livanta LLC is committed to providing access to all individuals who are seeking information from our website. To provide this information, the Livanta LLC website has been designed to comply with Section 508 of the Rehabilitation Act of 1973, as amended.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Section 508 is a federal law that requires certain information providers to provide individuals with disabilities equal access to electronic information comparable to those who do not have disabilities, subject to certain exceptions and exemptions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For information about the availability of auxiliary aids and services, please visit: <a href=\"https://www.medicare.gov/about-us/accessibility-nondiscrimination-notice\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.medicare.gov/about-us/accessibility-nondiscrimination-notice</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you require assistance or wish to report an issue related to the accessibility of any content on this website, please submit a notice through the <a href=\"file:///C:/OSPanel/domains/livanta.html/public/contacts.html\">Contact Us web form</a>. Please include the nature of the accessibility problem. If the accessibility problem involves a particular webpage, the message should include the URL (web address) of the page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Accessibility', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accessibility', '', '', '2024-01-03 20:45:33', '2024-01-03 20:45:33', '', 0, 'http://livanta.test/?page_id=217', 0, 'page', '', 0),
